# Git attributes for template repository
#
# Structure:
#   - bootstrap.sh          Entry point (kept)
#   - .template/            All template infrastructure (kept)
#     - docs/               Template documentation
#     - examples/           Reference examples
#     - config/             Version defaults
#     - scripts/            Template scripts
#     - configs/            Language config templates
#     - .devcontainer/      Devcontainer templates
#     - ...
#
# Users can re-run bootstrap.sh anytime to add languages or change settings.
